<div class="accordion-content" data-accordion-title="Details">- Model wears S and is 5'10<br />- 45% Cotton 55% Viscose<br />- Elasticated waist&nbsp;<br />- Full lining<br />- Side pockets<br />- Pairs with our Vera shirt</div>
<div class="accordion-content" data-accordion-title="Care">Spot cleaning recommended, or alternatively hand or machine wash with cool water. Lay flat or hang to dry.</div>
<div class="accordion-content" data-accordion-title="Sustainability">This is a woven fabric using 45% Cotton 55% Viscose. A sustainable duo, which combines perfectly to give a breathable and natural high quality finish. All of our fabrics are also 100% vegan and cruelty free.&nbsp;<br />
<p><br />We reccommend using a <a href="https://join-the-sisterhood.com/guppyfriend-wash-bag/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Guppyfriend wash bag</a> to wash this item.</p>
</div>
<div class="accordion-content" data-accordion-title="Shipping">We ship worldwide from the UK. All orders usually leave our warehouse within 24 hours (excluding weekends)&nbsp;<br />&nbsp;<br />UK DPD 1-2 Business days - &pound;5<br />(Usually shipped the same day if ordered before 1pm, excluding busy periods)&nbsp;<br /><br />Europe Standard Tracked 6-10 days - &euro;10<br />Europe DHL Express 1-2 days - &euro;15-20<br /><strong>All duties and taxes are included</strong><br /><br />USA Standard Tracked 10-20 days $10<br />USA DHL Express 3-5 days $15<br /><br />You can read more shipping information <a href="https://join-the-sisterhood.com/shipping/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">here</a>.&nbsp;</div>
<div class="accordion-content" data-accordion-title="Returns">We accept full priced, unworn items for a full refund if returned within 21 days from the ship date. Items from the sale section are eligable for exchange or store credit only. For our full returns policy click <a href="https://join-the-sisterhood.com/returns/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">here</a>.</div>
